casebody.data:
No. 1038,

Misc.

In re Blevins. Petitioner pro se. Thomas C. Lynch, Attorney General of California, and Albert W. Harris, Jr., and Michael R. Marrón, Deputy Attorneys General, for the State of California.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of habeas corpus denied. Treating the papers submitted as a petition for a writ of certio-rari, certiorari is denied.
